♫  The past is desolate  ♫

508
00:42:22,540 --> 00:42:27,280
♫  Waiting for the ride to the highest heaven  ♫

509
00:42:27,280 --> 00:42:30,280
♫  The ethereal fog  ♫

510
00:42:30,280 --> 00:42:34,820
♫  Fame and fortune do not matter to an enlightened person  ♫

511
00:42:34,820 --> 00:42:38,020
♫  I face the sun  ♫

